<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">We should be viewing ourselves this way on a regular basis.</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">When we see ourselves this way, then God gives us more strength to resist the temptations of sinful behavior.</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Would someone who claims sin to be dead in themselves advocate for as much freedom as possible for their fellow countrymen to sin themselves?</li></ul></body></html>